# Release Workflow

## Version Source of Truth
`ha-raumkernel-addon/config.yaml` is the **master version file**.

## Correct Steps for a New Version

### 1. Edit code & bump version in config.yaml
```yaml
version: "1.X.Y"
```

### 2. Run prepare-build.sh (ALWAYS — do not skip)
```bash
cd /home/holli/BUILD/ha-raumkernel
./ha-raumkernel-addon/prepare-build.sh
```
This script does three things in one shot:
- Updates `ha-raumkernel-addon/rootfs/app/package.json` and regenerates `package-lock.json` via `npm install --package-lock-only`
- Updates `custom_components/teufel_raumfeld_raumkernel/manifest.json`
- Copies the entire integration into `ha-raumkernel-addon/teufel_raumfeld_raumkernel/` (clean copy)

### 3. Update CHANGELOG.md
Add a `## 1.X.Y` entry at the top of `ha-raumkernel-addon/CHANGELOG.md`.

### 4. Commit ALL changed files, then push
```bash
git add -A
git commit -m "v1.X.Y — <short description>"
git push
```

## Files that must all show the same version
| File | Updated by |
|------|-----------|
| `ha-raumkernel-addon/config.yaml` | manual |
| `ha-raumkernel-addon/rootfs/app/package.json` | `sync-version.sh` (via prepare-build) |
| `ha-raumkernel-addon/rootfs/app/package-lock.json` | `npm install --package-lock-only` (via prepare-build) |
| `custom_components/teufel_raumfeld_raumkernel/manifest.json` | `sync-version.sh` (via prepare-build) |
| `ha-raumkernel-addon/teufel_raumfeld_raumkernel/manifest.json` | `cp` in prepare-build |

## ⚠️ Never do manually what prepare-build.sh does
Do not manually copy files or run `sync-integration.sh` as a substitute —
that script has different (and incomplete) behaviour.

## Troubleshooting: "dockerfile is missing" in HA Supervisor
This is a HA Supervisor data-corruption error unrelated to our code.
Fix: run `ha supervisor repair` on the HA instance.
